{"tid":2307312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"籲報料：微不足道資訊拼埋有用","createTime":"2020-12-01T05:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T07:24:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"37591e24221c68b79d40bbdb97f3e4e15a77db31","tid":2307312,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T05:57:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/R5KA7HBKBFG5LBES65OF7HACFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FR5KA7HBKBFG5LBES65OF7HACFE%2F&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0jbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=777d6169\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FR5KA7HBKBFG5LBES65OF7HACFE%2F&h=6efd2bde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/R5KA7HBKBFG5LBES65OF7HACFE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n籲報料：微不足道資訊拼埋有用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/e0QC_-L9EluQd6y8q4GsexAfVlg=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WUXIAANKBJDP7OXCSZIB4UQHLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fe0QC_-L9EluQd6y8q4GsexAfVlg%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWUXIAANKBJDP7OXCSZIB4UQHLU.jpg&h=6237e004&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■梓樂父親昨旁聽後離開法院。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】案發當晚在停車場發現梓樂的白帽男崔家朗昨日出庭作供，成為第二位響應梓樂爸爸呼籲，挺身出庭作供的市民。崔家朗作供完畢後在庭外表示，他知道早前的證供提及自己，認為有責任現身交代一些事情，不想尋找真相的過程中帶有遺憾。他亦呼籲知情者聯絡死因庭，「當好多嘅微不足道（的資訊）拼湊埋一齊，就係有用嘅資訊」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讚梓樂父母暖心<br />\n<br />\n崔家朗承認，現身法庭前內心亦有掙扎，「情感有好大嘅起伏，出嚟都用咗好多時間」。他明白現身作供不是容易的決定，但梓樂父母「真係好暖心」，呼籲任何資訊都可提供給梓樂爸爸或死因庭，明言「（資訊）幾微不足道都好，都希望你可以企出嚟」。<br />\n<br />\n崔又指，相信在過去一年間，很多香港人都經歷了相當痛苦的狀態，情緒會不自覺地起伏，腦海中亦會閃過一些片段，但「希望大家都可以照顧好自己，照顧好身邊嘅人，趁住呢個時間好好咁療傷」，將情緒轉化為力量，做自己喜歡做的事，。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"f7d9b837c1c68c4bf3ff190103023b07dbb5aa04","tid":2307312,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T07:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}